festival.introText:
The UK's biggest multi-venue dance music event returns to the city of Dundee to celebrate the 25th anniversary of the first event, with 200 DJs and artists performing in 29 venues from 12:30pm until 3:30am the next day.

The 4,000 capacity closing party will be held in Fat Sams (Aura Nightclub) with three floors and six rooms dedicated to DJs and artists playing the very best in house, tech house, techno, trance, old skool and anthems and classics.

faqs.question: When is Dundee Dance Event 2023?
faqs.answer: Dundee Dance Event takes place Sunday 30th April 2023.

faqs.question: How much are Dundee Dance Event tickets?
faqs.answer: Head to the tickets section to find out the latest ticket prices.

faqs.question: Where is Dundee Dance Event
faqs.answer: Dundee Dance Event is located at LIVE Fat Sams, Dundee.

faqs.question: What happens If I bought a ticket and cannot attend?
faqs.answer:
Unfortunately we can’t issue you with a refund if you can’t make the event due to work commitments or your mates have dropped out. In these circumstances, we advise passing on your tickets privately to avoid losing out on the money spent.

 

Refunds can only be offered if the event is cancelled or postponed, as agreed upon purchase.
